main event: An unidentified object was observed in the sky on 3 Nov 66 in Memphis, Tennessee.
interesting points: The report states that there have been several sightings of strange aerial phenomena in the Memphis area over the years., Observers included individuals with military and scientific backgrounds., The person reporting the sighting expressed willingness to provide more information on previous sightings., The report concluded that the data provided was insufficient for a scientific evaluation., There are no photographs or physical evidence included in the report.
witness description: A resident of Memphis indicating a willingness to share information about local UFO sightings.
